title: Repeated warning: dataset </supercontig_0/continuous> cannot be read, deflate filter is not available from genomedata-load

content.raw:
```shell
$ genomedata-load --sizes --sequence /home/mkarimzadeh/Documents/RunSegwayProtocol/Data/GRCh38_EBV.chrom.sizes.tsv --track H3K4me3=/home/mkarimzadeh/Documents/RunSegwayProtocol/Data/bedGraphs/MapFilteredBedGraphs/ENCFF151DIJ_MM.1S_H3K4me3_UmapFiltered.bedGraph /home/mkarimzadeh/Documents/RunSegwayProtocol/Data/GenomeDataArchives/ENCFF151DIJ_MM.1S_H3K4me3.genomedata


warning: dataset </supercontig_0/continuous> cannot be read, deflate filter is not available
(repeated)
```

This error does not occur when perform the 4 seperate steps for loading a genomedata archive (e.g. load-seq).
